message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I am furious! Your company has let me down big time.
I'm deeply sorry to hear that you're feeling this way. I'm here to help. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for completing security. Can you also confirm your date of birth?
That's all correct. Now, could you please provide me with the first line of your address and postcode?
Great, thank you. Lastly, could you confirm your email address?
Thank you for completing security. I understand you're upset. What seems to be the issue with your insurance?
I recently had an accident, and your company is refusing to cover the damages. This is unacceptable!
I'm sorry to hear about your situation. Let's see what we can do to help. A possible resolution could be to review the details of your claim together. Would that work for you?
I've already provided all the information multiple times, and no one seems to care. This is outrageous!
I completely understand your frustration. Let's try to reach a consensus on how to move forward. Can you please provide more details about the accident so we can investigate further?
I've had enough of this incompetence! I'll be taking my business elsewhere. This conversation has been a waste of time.

I'm sorry you feel that way. We value your feedback and apologize for any inconvenience caused. If you change your mind or need assistance in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance today. You are welcome.
